Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.05,0:00:20.68,taustaga,,0,0,0,,selles n√§gemuses n√§gi ta paavsti selja p√∂√∂ramist katoliku kirikule
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.22,0:00:24.39,taustaga,,0,0,0,,ja see oli seotud antikristuse t√µusuga
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.09,0:00:30.18,taustaga,,0,0,0,,m√µtlesin n√º√ºd sellele n√§gemusele aastaid, kui me l√§heneme 2024 aastale
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.58,0:00:35.98,taustaga,,0,0,0,,lihtsalt j√§lgides aastat 2023, et n√§ha, mis juhtub
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.88,0:00:42.48,taustaga,,0,0,0,,ma tahan, et Sa kuuleksid seda n√§gemust
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.22,0:00:45.51,taustaga,,0,0,0,,ma tahan, et Sa n√§eksid neid pealkirju
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.20,0:00:50.54,taustaga,,0,0,0,,h√ºva, siin on esmalt see n√§gemus
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.00,0:01:02.77,taustaga,,0,0,230,,Salvestatud 2020 aastal, ta sai s√µnumi Issandalt umbes aastal 2016.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.73,0:00:56.35,taustaga,,0,0,0,,See juhtus v√µibolla 3,5 aastat tagasi. Ma √ºtleks, et 3,5 aastat tagasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:04.12,taustaga,,0,0,0,,see oli nagu n√§gemus-unen√§gu ja ma ei saagi p√§ris t√§pselt aru, kumb see oli
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.32,0:01:06.36,taustaga,,0,0,0,,kuid ma usun, et see oli n√§gemus
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.71,0:01:13.58,taustaga,,0,0,0,,ma n√§gin ennast ja seisin v√§ga k√µrgel kaljul
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.04,0:01:19.18,taustaga,,0,0,0,,nagu kivi, see oli v√§ga k√µrgel, nagu riiul
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.50,0:01:25.80,taustaga,,0,0,0,,ma seisin seal ja vaatasin pealt, mis toimub
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.30,0:01:35.41,taustaga,,0,0,0,,ma n√§gin teda seismas ja tean, et see oli tema
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.90,0:01:38.10,taustaga,,0,0,0,,ta oli pika r√º√ºga ja k√µige juurdekuuluvaga
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.22,0:01:48.19,taustaga,,0,0,0,,ja ta vaatas neid inimesi, nad karjusid, nutsid, leinasid ja olid v√§ga √§rritunud,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.49,0:01:52.60,taustaga,,0,0,0,,sest ta p√∂√∂ras √ºmber ja keeras neile selja
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.12,0:01:56.50,taustaga,,0,0,0,,ta p√∂√∂ras t√§ielikult selja katoliku kirikule
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.85,0:02:05.32,taustaga,,0,0,0,,need inimesed, nii kaugele kui oli n√§ha, seal oli nagu miljon inimest all maapinnal
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.63,0:02:10.50,taustaga,,0,0,0,,paavst oli k√µrgel kivil ja ma vaatasin teda sealt
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:14.90,taustaga,,0,0,0,,ta p√∂√∂ras neile inimestele t√§ielikult selja

Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.33,0:02:32.23,taustaga,,0,0,0,,ma n√§gin seda tulnukat meie vahele tulemas
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:36.40,taustaga,,0,0,0,,ta tuli paavsti ja minu vahele rahva sekka
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.97,0:02:47.18,taustaga,,0,0,0,,ta hakkas r√§√§kima ja ta oli hirmus, ta oli nagu draakon, nagu antikristus, olen selles kindel
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.43,0:02:54.48,taustaga,,0,0,0,,ja ta hakkas r√§√§kima ja inimesed l√µpetasid nutmise
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.16,0:03:02.30,taustaga,,0,0,0,,ja nad p√∂√∂rasid oma n√§od √ºles ja nad vaatasid √ºles kaljule ja paavstile - me m√µlemad olime veel seal √ºleval
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:11.00,taustaga,,0,0,0,,ja nad v√µtsid ta vastu ja plaksutasid ja armastasid teda
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:22.06,taustaga,,0,0,0,,nad hakkavad teda.. vastu v√µtma v√µi mis see s√µna tegelikult oleks

Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.89,0:04:47.60,taustaga,,0,0,50,,see, mis just juhtus, sellel on tagaj√§rjed tulevikule, isegi l√µpuaegade jaoks

Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.98,0:05:32.54,taustaga,,0,0,0,,et see viidatakse olemuslikult kui korralagedus, mis on vastuolus loomuliku √µigusega kui r√§nk k√µlvatus

Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:49.21,valge suur kiri paksu taustaga,,0,0,100,,TERVE VIDEO\NVAATAMISEKS\NMINE SIIA:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:51.18,taustaga,,0,0,220,,Jonathan Cahn'i prohvetlik s√µnum:\Npaavst Franciscuse l√µpuaja √§rataganemine
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:56.30,taustaga,,0,0,0,,s√µbrad, ma usun, et me oleme v√§ga, v√§ga prohvetlikus ajaaknas
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.44,0:06:14.58,taustaga,,0,0,0,,see on esimene kord 2000 aasta jooksul kui midagi sellist juhtub
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:27.38,taustaga,,0,0,0,,meil on kogu maailmas pealkirjades valimisaasta, mida loetakse nagu Piibli prohvetiennustuse viimaseid lehek√ºlgi
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:37.58,taustaga,,0,0,0,,me usume Jh 14:1-3 seda, et teatud ajal tulevikus kavatseb Jeesus oma koguduse sellelt planeedilt eemaldada
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:40.38,taustaga,,0,0,0,,kohta, mille Ta on meile ette valmistanud
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:44.34,taustaga,,0,0,0,,Sellest ei saa esmalt kuidagi m√∂√∂da. See juhtub.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:51.35,taustaga,,0,0,0,,Sa saad olla n√µustudes v√µtma vastu Jeesuse Kristuse oma s√ºdames. √útle lihtsalt lihtne palve:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.77,0:06:56.13,taustaga,,0,0,0,,Ma tulen praegu Sinu ette ja h√º√ºan Sinu nime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:07:00.40,taustaga,,0,0,0,,Ma usun, et Sa surid ristil minu eest ja t√µusid surnuist √ºles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:04.70,taustaga,,0,0,0,,Ma palun Sind, p√§√§sta mind ja pese mind ristil valatud veres

Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:10.51,taustaga,,0,0,0,,Nii lihtne see ongi. Kui sa m√µtled seda oma s√ºdames,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:13.10,taustaga,,0,0,0,,oled Sa p√§√§stetud! See on su esimene samm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:19.25,taustaga,,0,0,0,,Pane Piibel ja palve oma p√§eva  t√§htsaimaks osaks

fXTvKsmU,De shaw SI disc prob 1,Tipsy_agate,Python,Sunday 14th of January 2024 09:04:29 PM CDT,"These question was asked in D.E Shaw assessment
Considering a lane to be one-dimensional, you are provided with an array police_station consisting of n distinct integers representing the coordinates of police stations.

You, as a prosperous individual, aspire to acquire exactly capacity distinct properties across the entirety of this one-dimensional lane (which may be located anywhere on the number line), with the condition that they do not coincide with the coordinates of any police station and neither any older property acquired.

The cost associated with purchasing a property is determined by its minimum distance from any police station. The total cost incurred will be the sum of costs associated with purchasing each property. Here distance between x1 and x2 means the absolute difference of x1 and x2.(= (|x1-x2|)

Given police_station an array containing the coordinates of the police stations, and capacity indicates the total number of distinct properties you can acquire. Your task iso calculate the total minimum cost to acquire exactly the capacity number of properties.
Suppose n = 2, police_station = [7, 8], and capacity = 4. The coordinates of your property will be [5, 6, 9, 10] for minimum cost. So, the answer is sum of |7-5|+ |7-6 + |8-9|+|8-10| = 6.
Complete the function minAcquire Cost in the editor below.
int police_station[n]: the input array police station containing the coordinates of all the police stations.
int capacity: the number of properties you want to buy
long int: the minimum cost of buying all the properties
jb2p9mmU,De shaw SI disc prob 2,Tipsy_agate,Python,Sunday 14th of January 2024 09:03:57 PM CDT,"*PROBLEM 2*
Given an array arr of n positive integers and an integer val. We can perform the following operation of the given array arr at most once. The operation is as follows.
1. Choose two indices left and right such that left <= right and right <=(1-based indexing).

2. For each value in the range of indices left and right, bit-wise xor each of them with m (m is a non-negative integer which you can choose as per your subarray). More formally nums[i] will change to (nums[i] xor m).
Find the maximum possible frequency of val after performing the operation at most once.
There are 6 possible (left, right) pairs such that left <= right and right <= n
‚Ä¢ (1,1) We can use m = 5. The resultant array will be [2, 2, 3]. (Frequency of valis 2)
‚Ä¢ (1,2) We can use m = 0. The resultant array will be [7, 2, 3]. (Frequency of val is 1)
(1,3) We can use m = 0. The resultant array will be [7
‚Ä¢ (1,3) We can use m = 0. The resultant array will be [7
‚Ä¢ (2,2)-> We can use m = 0. The resultant array will be [7, 2. 31. (Frequency of valis 1)
‚Ä¢ (2,3) -> We can use m = 0. The resultant array will be [7, 2, 3]. (Frequency of valis 1)
‚Ä¢ (3,3) We can use m = 1. The resultant array will be [7. 2. 2). (Frequency of val is 2)
The maximum frequency of val which we can get is 2.
Would Love to know approaches to these problems"
